About
$
$
$
Welcome to Barbecue Beer Co., Jensen Beach's newest hotspot for barbecue lovers and beer enthusiasts alike. Nestled in the heart of Florida's Treasure Coast, we offer a vibrant atmosphere where good times meet great flavors. Our full bar boasts an impressive selection of craft beers and cocktails, perfect for pairing with our mouthwatering barbecue specialties. Join us for live music nights, where local talent sets the stage for unforgettable evenings. Whether you're here for the food, the drinks, or the music, Barbecue Beer Co. promises an experience worth savoring.
